snippet.title: Shrot - reveal
snippet.description:
Shrot is a bite-sized old-school action RTS set on a sandy planet with horses, tractors and techno music.

The game draws inspiration from Paranoia, a Czech remake of Dune 2 and the third real-time strategy game ever made, released only in the Czech Republic in 1995.
